## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data. Some sources may present biased views based on personal opinions or specific contexts. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of technology means that new developments could alter the current understanding of its impact. The report relies on publicly available information, which may not capture all dimensions of the issue.